    <item>
      <title>中国企业大举押注欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/chinese-companies-are-betting-big-on-the-euros-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英格兰男子足球队将于周日在柏林举行的 2024 年欧洲杯决赛中对阵西班牙队。领先的中国公司正在利用广告曝光率，在赛事中投放大量广告。彭博社的 Catherine Lim 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/chinese-companies-are-betting-big-on-the-euros-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 08:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称，Business Insider 老板 Axel Springer 正在考虑分拆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/business-insider-owner-axel-springer-is-said-to-weigh-split</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，拥有 Politico 和 Business Insider 的德国媒体集团 Axel Springer SE 的所有者正在讨论将公司的媒体资产从其数字广告和分类广告业务中分离出来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/business-insider-owner-axel-springer-is-said-to-weigh-split</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 08:15:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
