    <item>
      <title>瑞银因担忧反弹而下调特斯拉评级，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/tesla-downgraded-by-ubs-on-concern-over-ai-driven-share-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司股价下跌，此前瑞银集团下调了其股票评级，理由是人们担心这家电动汽车制造商的股价因对其人工智能计划的乐观情绪而“上涨过多、过快”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/tesla-downgraded-by-ubs-on-concern-over-ai-driven-share-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 07:31:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员押注降息，美国国债抹去 2024 年的损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/treasuries-wipe-out-this-year-s-loss-as-traders-bet-on-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀降温增强了对美联储降息的押注，美国国债已经抹去了今年的跌幅，投资者目前转向生产者价格来确认通货紧缩趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/treasuries-wipe-out-this-year-s-loss-as-traders-bet-on-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 05:06:58 GMT</pubDate>
